[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]是第102個[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]的[[奥斯卡最佳國際影片獎|最佳國際影片獎]]競賽國。奧斯卡最佳外語片獎由[[美國電影藝術與科學學院|美國電影藝術與科學學院]]頒發，為[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]中頒發給年度美國以外最佳非英語電影的獎項<ref name="Rules">{{cite web | title = Rule Thirteen: Special Rules for the Foreign Language Film Award | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | publisher = [[Academy_of_Motion_Picture_Arts_and_Sciences|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/rules/86/rule13.html | accessdate = 2013-08-26 | archive-date = 2013-07-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130730051948/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/rules/86/rule13.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。該獎項原名為「奧斯卡最佳外語片獎」，但學院認為「外語」該詞已過時，所以於2019年4月更名為「最佳國際影片獎」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |title=Academy Announces Rule Changes For 92nd Oscars |work=Forbes |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archive-date=2019-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527181952/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=ACADEMY ANNOUNCES RULES FOR 92ND OSCARS |url=https://www.oscars.org/news/academy-announces-rules-92nd-oscars |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=Oscars.org {{!}} Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |date=2019-04-23 |language=en |archive-date=2019-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711223230/https://www.oscars.org/news/academy-announces-rules-92nd-oscars |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=options |first1=Show more sharing |last2=URLCopied! |first2=Copy Link |title=Film academy is setting new inclusion standards for Oscars eligibility |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-06-12/film-academy-announces-new-inclusion-initiatives-systemic-racism |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2020-06-12 |archive-date=2021-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712145159/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-06-12/film-academy-announces-new-inclusion-initiatives-systemic-racism |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Lawler |first1=Kelly |title=Academy to implement diversity standards for Oscars eligibility, set best picture at 10 nominees |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2020/06/12/oscars-academy-implementing-diversity-standards-eligibility/3174801001/ |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=USA TODAY |archive-date=2021-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210829090110/https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2020/06/12/oscars-academy-implementing-diversity-standards-eligibility/3174801001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |title=Academy Announces Rule Changes For 92nd Oscars |work=Forbes |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archive-date=2020-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512231634/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

至2012年來，馬來西亞已派出兩部影片參加奧斯卡金像獎最佳外語片獎。第一部《金山公主》參賽片是馬來西亞歷史上最昂貴的電影。<ref> {{cite web |url=http://www.sinemamalaysia.com.my/main/index.php?mod=newspaper&id=1382 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219204806/http://www.sinemamalaysia.com.my/main/index.php?mod=newspaper&id=1382 |archivedate=2012-02-19 }} </ref>

